{"title":"Hope Union Clipless Pedals spin out dual-clip mechanism for easy entry, tuneable release","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/08/03/hope-union-clipless-pedals-spin-out-dual-clip-mechanism-for-easy-entry-tuneable-release/","date":1627977630000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Hope Technology have released three new clipless pedals for mountain biking, utilizing an all-new dual clip mechanism that uses its own specific cleat and is not cross compatible with other clipless systems. The new mechanism is primarily designed for easy entry, with two cleat options offering different degrees of free float, release angles and effort required to unclip. Here’s all you need to know about the Hope Union Clipless Pedals.</p><figure id=\"attachment_266965\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-266965\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073847/hope-union-rc-clipless-pedal-xc-mtb-blue.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073847/hope-union-rc-clipless-pedal-xc-mtb-blue.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb28/ng:webp/ngcb28\" alt=\"hope union clipless pedal mtb race rc model blue 55mm q-factor titanium axle\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073847/hope-union-rc-clipless-pedal-xc-mtb-blue.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073847/hope-union-rc-clipless-pedal-xc-mtb-blue-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073847/hope-union-rc-clipless-pedal-xc-mtb-blue-800x533.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073847/hope-union-rc-clipless-pedal-xc-mtb-blue-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073847/hope-union-rc-clipless-pedal-xc-mtb-blue-768x512.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073847/hope-union-rc-clipless-pedal-xc-mtb-blue-696x464.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073847/hope-union-rc-clipless-pedal-xc-mtb-blue-1068x712.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073847/hope-union-rc-clipless-pedal-xc-mtb-blue-630x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073847/hope-union-rc-clipless-pedal-xc-mtb-blue.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb28/ng:webp/ngcb28\" ezoid=\"0.09510845951898395\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073847/hope-union-rc-clipless-pedal-xc-mtb-blue.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073847/hope-union-rc-clipless-pedal-xc-mtb-blue-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073847/hope-union-rc-clipless-pedal-xc-mtb-blue-800x533.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073847/hope-union-rc-clipless-pedal-xc-mtb-blue-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073847/hope-union-rc-clipless-pedal-xc-mtb-blue-768x512.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073847/hope-union-rc-clipless-pedal-xc-mtb-blue-696x464.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073847/hope-union-rc-clipless-pedal-xc-mtb-blue-1068x712.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073847/hope-union-rc-clipless-pedal-xc-mtb-blue-630x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb28 630w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-266965\">All Hope Union Clipless Pedals run a 55mm Q-Factor… what’s that? Learn more <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/02/21/aasq-look-xpedo-get-a-foothold-on-the-pedal-questions-burning-at-your-sole/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">here</a>.</figcaption></figure><p>The new Union Race, Union Trail and Union Gravity clipless pedals for Hope Technology all run the same dual-clip mechanism, an entirely new clipless mechanism that isn’t compatible with any other mountain bike cleat on the market. Before we get into how it works, we wanted to know <em>why</em> Hope thought a new clipless mechanism was necessary.</p><p><em>“We didn’t set out to develop a new system but it naturally developed this way. We have made flat pedals for a number of years but the majority of us at the factory ride clips so it seemed a shame we couldn’t use our own pedals. Basically, we wanted to stick a clip mechanism on an F20. When we looked at our options the only existing system available to us would be based on a Shimano SPD, however this system doesn’t work too well when used with a big platform, it needs clearance meaning most of the platform would be wasted. We made some prototypes of our own mechanism which solved some of the issues and it worked pretty well first time so that gave us confidence to develop it further and see where it took us”</em> – Sam Gibbs, Hope Technology’s designer of the Union Pedals.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073853/hope-union-trail-clipless-pedal-mountain-biking.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073853/hope-union-trail-clipless-pedal-mountain-biking.jpg\" alt=\"hope union tc mtb pedal red cr-mo axle 4 pins each side\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073853/hope-union-trail-clipless-pedal-mountain-biking.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073853/hope-union-trail-clipless-pedal-mountain-biking-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073853/hope-union-trail-clipless-pedal-mountain-biking-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073853/hope-union-trail-clipless-pedal-mountain-biking-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073853/hope-union-trail-clipless-pedal-mountain-biking-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073853/hope-union-trail-clipless-pedal-mountain-biking-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073853/hope-union-trail-clipless-pedal-mountain-biking-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073853/hope-union-trail-clipless-pedal-mountain-biking-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073853/hope-union-trail-clipless-pedal-mountain-biking.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073853/hope-union-trail-clipless-pedal-mountain-biking.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073853/hope-union-trail-clipless-pedal-mountain-biking-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073853/hope-union-trail-clipless-pedal-mountain-biking-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073853/hope-union-trail-clipless-pedal-mountain-biking-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073853/hope-union-trail-clipless-pedal-mountain-biking-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073853/hope-union-trail-clipless-pedal-mountain-biking-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073853/hope-union-trail-clipless-pedal-mountain-biking-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073853/hope-union-trail-clipless-pedal-mountain-biking-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a>The new mechanism design aims to provide easy pedal entry combined with secure cleat holding and positive release characteristics. The dual clip mechanism means the front clip can move on pedal entry to reduce the effort required to clip into the pedal. It also flattens the entry angle of the shoe, giving a wider cleat acceptance angle and allowing the front of the shoe sole to run closer to the pedal body for increased stability. Cleat release is driven off fixed pins for a positive and consistent release.</p><p><a href=\"https:/