7/30073841/hope-union-gravity-clipless-pedal-downhill-enduro-mtb-black-100x70.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073841/hope-union-gravity-clipless-pedal-downhill-enduro-mtb-black.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073841/hope-union-gravity-clipless-pedal-downhill-enduro-mtb-black.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073841/hope-union-gravity-clipless-pedal-downhill-enduro-mtb-black-297x207.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073841/hope-union-gravity-clipless-pedal-downhill-enduro-mtb-black-800x557.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073841/hope-union-gravity-clipless-pedal-downhill-enduro-mtb-black-120x84.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073841/hope-union-gravity-clipless-pedal-downhill-enduro-mtb-black-768x534.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073841/hope-union-gravity-clipless-pedal-downhill-enduro-mtb-black-696x484.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073841/hope-union-gravity-clipless-pedal-downhill-enduro-mtb-black-1068x743.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073841/hope-union-gravity-clipless-pedal-downhill-enduro-mtb-black-604x420.jpg 604w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30073841/hope-union-gravity-clipless-pedal-downhill-enduro-mtb-black-100x70.jpg 100w\"></a></p><p>The Union Pedal bodies are CNC machined from billet. All are designed to maximize the contact area at the shoe/cleat interface and pedal body for increased stability and power transfer. The contact area combines cleat-to-stop-plate contact and shoe-sole-to-pedal-body contact for a solid under-foot feel.</p><div><figure id=\"attachment_266967\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-266967\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30074226/hope-union-cleat-number-4.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30074226/hope-union-cleat-number-4.jpg\" alt=\"hope union cleat number 4\" width=\"1200\" height=\"680\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30074226/hope-union-cleat-number-4.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30074226/hope-union-cleat-number-4-297x168.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30074226/hope-union-cleat-number-4-800x453.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30074226/hope-union-cleat-number-4-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30074226/hope-union-cleat-number-4-768x435.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30074226/hope-union-cleat-number-4-696x394.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30074226/hope-union-cleat-number-4-1068x605.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30074226/hope-union-cleat-number-4-741x420.jpg 741w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30074226/hope-union-cleat-number-4.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30074226/hope-union-cleat-number-4.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30074226/hope-union-cleat-number-4-297x168.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30074226/hope-union-cleat-number-4-800x453.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30074226/hope-union-cleat-number-4-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30074226/hope-union-cleat-number-4-768x435.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30074226/hope-union-cleat-number-4-696x394.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30074226/hope-union-cleat-number-4-1068x605.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30074226/hope-union-cleat-number-4-741x420.jpg 741w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-266967\">The Number 4 Union Cleat; the cleat and clip components are made from stainless steel so they shouldn’t corrode</figcaption></figure></div><p>All Hope Union clipless pedals are supplied with two cleat options. The Number 4 cleat gives 4° of free float (the amount of angular float before the cleat starts to disengage with the mechanism) and has a 12° release angle. The Number 5 cleat gives 5° of free float and has a 13° release angle. It also requires more effort to release, suited to more aggressive riding. Both cleats also allow 2mm of lateral (side to side) float.</p><p>The Hope Union Race, Trail and Gravity clipless pedals all run the same internals as Hope’s F20 flat pedal. That’s three cartridge bearings and a norglide bush for smooth long term durability. Axle service kits are available at £16.75 per pedal.</p><h3>What MTB Shoes do the Hope Union Pedals work with?</h3><p>We asked designer Sam Gibbs, exactly that. He shied away from mentioning any particular brands, but he did tells us the Hope Union Clipless Pedals are optimised to work with a 7mm deep cleat box, stating that “any shoe around this number will work nicely without cleat shims or spacers on the pedal itself”.&nbsp;</p><p>Shoes with a deeper cleat box would need shims under the cleats; these are provided with the pedals. On the other hand, shoes with a shallower cleat box would need the pedal pins to be made taller with spacers (also provided) to get contact with the shoe sole.</p><h4>Union Race Clip</h4><figure id=\"attachment_266968\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-266968\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075727/hope-race-clip-union-pedals-xc-endurance-mtb-riding.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075727/hope-race-clip-union-pedals-xc-endurance-mtb-riding.jpg\" alt=\"hope union rc xc mtb pedals\" width=\"1200\" height=\"494\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075727/hope-race-clip-union-pedals-xc-endurance-mtb-riding.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075727/hope-race-clip-union-pedals-xc-endurance-mtb-riding-297x122.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075727/hope-race-clip-union-pedals-xc-endurance-mtb-riding-800x329.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075727/hope-race-clip-union-pedals-xc-endurance-mtb-riding-120x49.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075727/hope-race-clip-union-pedals-xc-endurance-mtb-riding-768x316.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075727/hope-race-clip-union-pedals-xc-endurance-mtb-riding-696x287.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075727/hope-race-clip-union-pedals-xc-endurance-mtb-riding-1068x440.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075727/hope-race-clip-union-pedals-xc-endurance-mtb-riding-1020x420.jpg 1020w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075727/hope-race-clip-union-pedals-xc-endurance-mtb-riding.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075727/hope-race-clip-union-pedals-xc-endurance-mtb-riding.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075727/hope-race-clip-union-pedals-xc-endurance-mtb-riding-297x122.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075727/hope-race-clip-union-pedals-xc-endurance-mtb-riding-800x329.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075727/hope-race-clip-union-pedals-xc-endurance-mtb-riding-120x49.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075727/hope-race-clip-union-pedals-xc-endurance-mtb-riding-768x316.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075727/hope-race-clip-union-pedals-xc-endurance-mtb-riding-696x287.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075727/hope-race-clip-union-pedals-xc-endurance-mtb-riding-1068x440.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075727/hope-race-clip-union-pedals-xc-endurance-mtb-riding-1020x420.jpg 1020w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-266968\">The Hope Union Race clip has the following dimensions: 63mm Wide x 44mm Long</figcaption></figure><p>The Hope Union RC is the smallest, most lightweight of the three models, and runs a titanium axle as standard. A pair weigh in at a claimed 324g. The lack of platform and pedal pins pushes this one towards the realms of XC and endurance racing.&nbsp;</p><h4>Union Trail Clip</h4><figure id=\"attachment_266970\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-266970\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075738/hope-union-trail-clip-pedals-six-anodized-colors-cnc-machined-pedal-bodies.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075738/hope-union-trail-clip-pedals-six-anodized-colors-cnc-machined-pedal-bodies.jpg\" alt=\"hope union tc trail mtb clipless pedals\" width=\"1200\" height=\"740\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075738/hope-union-trail-clip-pedals-six-anodized-colors-cnc-machined-pedal-bodies.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075738/hope-union-trail-clip-pedals-six-anodized-colors-cnc-machined-pedal-bodies-297x183.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/30075738/hope-union-trail-clip-pedals-six-anodized-colors-cnc-machined-pedal-bodies-800x493.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/