USD</li><li>Union TC – £150, €185, $190 USD</li><li>Union GC – £160, €195, $200 USD</li></ul><p>All are available to order with first deliveries scheduled for September.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.hopetech.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>HopeTech.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"45524c5f46002efccc35b8bbdbfbda156672089f40ef430728bc4ef397e5d942","category":"Cycling"}